game.name: Sisters School Day
game.description:
Ellie and her little cute sister Annie look pretty excited for the first day in their school. Like many other kids, they want to dress them up with the best school uniforms and look awesome on their first day in school. Ellie studies in college while Annie has to prepare for the second grade. They look pretty confused what outfits fit into their needs the most. Can you help them out? Join Sisters School Day and be prepared to guide them to pick up the best school uniforms in the shortest time possible!

These two pretty girls have full faith on your fashion sense, so feel free to mix and match as many uniforms as you can in this brand new dressing game. Start with Ellie by helping her to pick up the nice school dress! Give her a green check short dress with a red belt on the waist and a red tie on a white shirt or a purple frock with a blue belt and a blue tie with a white shirt! You can also choose a black t-shirt with a light blue shrug and a pink muffler with white lines and pair it with a black short with blue button and a purple note.

Combine her look with a nice pair of shoes along with a matching school bag and get ready to turn now towards her younger sister Annie! Try to use as many outfits as you can to create the best school uniform for her little sister in this one of the best HTML5 girls games! Give her a blue check shirt with an orange and blue sweater and combine it with a blue short pant with two notes sticking on both sides! Complete her look with a lovely bag, a pair of sunglasses and a cute cat style headband! Try out more fashion games for kids on atmegame.com and have fun without download!
